<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Support</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/styles.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #555;
    }
    ul {
      text-align: left;
      list-style-type: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }
    li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    a:hover {
      color: #0056b3;
    }
    .image-container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    .image {
      max-width: 100%;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Support</h1>
    <p>Need help? We're here for you! Our goal is to make your stay comfortable and hassle-free.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/">View Occupied Rooms</a> - Check out our guests and see who's staying with us.</li>
      <li><a href="/checkin">Check In</a> - Ready to explore our rooms? Start your journey here.</li>
      <li><a href="/checkout">Check Out</a> - Time to say goodbye? Use this link for a smooth departure.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>For any inquiries or assistance, our front desk is available 24/7. Feel free to <a href="tel:+1234567890">call us</a> anytime!</p>
    <div class="image-container">
      <img class="image" src="/staff.jpg" alt="Friendly Hotel Staff">
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
